name: Summertime
comments: My favourite version of this song.
the greats just stand and deliver...no hype needed to carry them along (3) ....and without a doubt...among jazz divas...ms ella was "the greatest"...

Sou um dos milhõe que ainda sabem ouvir Summertime e Ella. Nem tudo está perdido nessa massificação, sem qualidade, na música de nossos dias. Para nosso alívio existe a tecnologia de uma emissora como LAST FM. Não nos renderemos...Jamais!!! Clóvis Assmann - Praia da Barra - Garopaba , Brasil.
Brings me to tears it's so lovely. I just sit back and luxuriate while listening to this.
Holy Moly this is one smokey version!
I absolutely agree with the last post ........ pure, simple & beautiful ... no more to be said - sit back and enjoy
Like I've said before, the Greats just stand and deliver. No hype needed to carry them along.
